              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Windows</h3>
            <p>Windows 10/11 (x64)</p>
            <code class="install-cmd">dotnet tool install --global TGit</code>
            <a href="#windows-install" class="download-btn">Installation Guide</a>
          </div>

