            <h3>Linux</h3>
            <p>Ubuntu, Debian, Fedora, etc.</p>
            <code class="install-cmd">dotnet tool install --global TGit</code>
            <a href="#linux-install" class="download-btn">Installation Guide</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="windows-install">
        <h2>Windows Installation</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install .NET 9.0 SDK</h4>
              <p>Download and install from <a href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download/dotnet/9.0" target="_blank">dotnet.microsoft.com</a></p>
              <p>Or use winget:</p>
              <pre><code>winget install Microsoft.DotNet.SDK.9</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install TGit</h4>
              <pre><code>dotnet tool install --global TGit</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Configure (Optional)</h4>
              <p>Set your dashboard URL:</p>
              <pre><code>set TGIT_API_URL=https://your-dashboard.com/api/git-activity</code></pre>
              <p>Add to your system environment variables for persistence.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="macos-install">
        <h2>macOS Installation</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install .NET 9.0 SDK</h4>
              <p>Using Homebrew:</p>
              <pre><code>brew install dotnet-sdk</code></pre>
              <p>Or download from <a href="https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download/dotnet/9.0" target="_blank">dotnet.microsoft.com</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install TGit</h4>
              <pre><code>dotnet tool install --global TGit</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Add to PATH</h4>
              <p>Add the .NET tools directory to your shell profile:</p>
              <pre><code>echo 'export PATH="$PATH:$HOME/.dotnet/tools"' >> ~/.zshrc
source ~/.zshrc</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Configure (Optional)</h4>
              <pre><code>export TGIT_API_URL=https://your-dashboard.com/api/git-activity</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="linux-install">
        <h2>Linux Installation</h2>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install .NET 9.0 SDK</h4>
              <p><strong>Ubuntu/Debian:</strong></p>
              <pre><code>sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install -y dotnet-sdk-9.0</code></pre>
              <p><strong>Fedora:</strong></p>
              <pre><code>sudo dnf install dotnet-sdk-9.0</code></pre>
              <p>Or see <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/core/install/linux" target="_blank">Microsoft's Linux installation guide</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install TGit</h4>
              <pre><code>dotnet tool install --global TGit</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Add to PATH</h4>
              <pre><code>echo 'export PATH="$PATH:$HOME/.dotnet/tools"' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Configure (Optional)</h4>
              <pre><code>export TGIT_API_URL=https://your-dashboard.com/api/git-activity</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="usage">
        <h2>Usage</h2>
        <p>Use <code>tgit</code> exactly like you would use <code>git</code>. All commands are passed through transparently:</p>
        
        <div class="usage-examples">
          <div class="example">
            <h4>Basic Commands</h4>
            <pre><code># Check status (tracked)
tgit status

# Stage files (tracked)
tgit add .

# Commit changes (tracked)
tgit commit -m "Your message"

# Push to remote
tgit push

# Pull latest
tgit pull</code></pre>
          </div>

          <div class="example">
            <h4>All Git Commands Work</h4>
            <pre><code># Create branches
tgit checkout -b feature/new-feature

# View history
tgit log --oneline

# Stash changes
tgit stash

# Any git command works!
tgit [any git command]</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tracked-commands">
          <h4>Tracked Commands</h4>
          <p>The following commands trigger activity updates to the dashboard:</p>
          <div class="command-tags">
            <span class="tag">status</span>
            <span class="tag">add</span>
            <span class="tag">commit</span>
            <span class="tag">restore</span>
            <span class="tag">checkout</span>
            <span class="tag">switch</span>
            <span class="tag">reset</span>
            <span class="tag">stash</span>
            <span class="tag">merge</span>
            <span class="tag">rebase</span>
            <span class="tag">cherry-pick</span>
            <span class="tag">revert</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="configuration">
        <h2>Configuration</h2>
        <p>TGit can be configured using environment variables:</p>
        
        <table class="config-table">
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Variable</th>
              <th>Description</th>
              <th>Default</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td><code>TGIT_API_URL</code></td>
              <td>The URL of your TGit dashboard API endpoint</td>
              <td><code>http://localhost:4321/api/git-activity</code></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="self-hosting">
        <h2>Self-Hosting the Dashboard</h2>
        <p>The TGit dashboard is built with Astro and can be self-hosted:</p>
        
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Clone the Repository</h4>
              <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/your-org/tgit.git
cd tgit/web</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Install Dependencies</h4>
              <pre><code>npm install</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Run Development Server</h4>
              <pre><code>npm run dev</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h4>Build for Production</h4>
              <pre><code>npm run build
npm run preview</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>TGit v{currentVersion} ‚Ä¢ Built with ‚ù§Ô∏è for developer teams</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .top-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .nav-link {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .nav-link.active {
    background: var(--accent-blue);
    color: white;
  }

  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .logo-large {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .version {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .content {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    scroll-margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .section p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .section a {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .features {
